B.aqA=new A.dh("What is TableLab?","TableLab is a poker tracking and analysis app for serious players. Log every session you play, review performance trends, record and replay hands for study, and build a personal database of opponent reads \u2014 all synced to the cloud across devices.")
B.aqV=new A.dh("Do I need an account to use the app?","Yes. TableLab uses a secure cloud backend so your data is always backed up and accessible from any device. You can sign in with Google (one tap) or create a traditional email/password account.")
B.aqH=new A.dh("How do I navigate the app?","The bottom navigation bar has five tabs: Dashboard, Sessions, Hands, Equity Calculator, and Reads. Tap the menu icon (\u2630) in the top-left to open the side panel for your profile, settings, help, and more.")
B.aqM=new A.dh("Is my data private?","Yes. Every query to the database enforces Row-Level Security \u2014 meaning you can only ever read or write your own data. No other user can see your sessions, hands, or reads.")
B.a3g=s([B.aqA,B.aqV,B.aqH,B.aqM],t.Bt)
